      <title>持不同政见的俄罗斯摇滚乐队面临被泰国驱逐出境</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/dissident-russian-rock-band-faces-deportation-thailand-2024-01-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几名官员周一告诉路透社，批评乌克兰战争的持不同政见的俄罗斯摇滚乐队成员因未经许可在普吉岛度假胜地被捕后，可能面临被泰国驱逐回国的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/dissident-russian-rock-band-faces-deportation-thailand-2024-01-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 12:20:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
