      <title>巴基斯坦央行将利率维持在22%，上调通胀预测</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/pakistan-central-bank-holds-key-rate-22-says-inflation-still-high-2024-01-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦央行周一连续第五次政策会议将关键利率维持在22%，并上调了全年通胀预测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/pakistan-central-bank-holds-key-rate-22-says-inflation-still-high-2024-01-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 12:02:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>孟加拉国报告今年首例尼帕病毒死亡病例</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/bangladesh-reports-first-death-nipah-virus-this-year-2024-01-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国周一报告了今年首例因尼帕病毒导致大脑损伤的死亡病例，一名男子在饮用生枣汁后死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/bangladesh-reports-first-death-nipah-virus-this-year-2024-01-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 11:17:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国护照持有者可以免签前往哪些国家？</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/which-countries-can-chinese-passport-holders-visit-without-visa-2024-01-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国因新冠肺炎 (COVID-19) 自我隔离三年，并于 2023 年重新开放边境，并与部分国家签署了免签证协议，以鼓励其公民旅行，这对吸引中国游客的外国目的地来说是一个福音。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/which-countries-can-chinese-passport-holders-visit-without-visa-2024-01-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 10:30:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国恒大承认香港法院的清算令</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-evergrande-acknowledges-hk-court-order-liquidate-2024-01-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国恒大周一承认，香港法院下令对这家全球负债最重的房地产开发商进行清算，原因是该公司在拖欠债券两年多后未能提供具体的重组计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-evergrande-acknowledges-hk-court-order-liquidate-2024-01-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 10:09:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对冲资金流 对冲基金以五年来最快速度买入中国股票 - 高盛</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/hedge-flow-hedge-funds-lap-up-china-stocks-fastest-pace-5-years-goldman-2024-01-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛在给客户的一份报告中写道，对冲基金上周三天内以五年多来最快的速度抢购遭受重创的中国股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/hedge-flow-hedge-funds-lap-up-china-stocks-fastest-pace-5-years-goldman-2024-01-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 10:06:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>东盟外长支持“缅甸拥有和领导”的危机解决方案</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asean-foreign-ministers-back-myanmar-owned-led-solution-crisis-2024-01-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[东南亚各国外长周一敦促结束缅甸的血腥危机，并表示一致支持东盟和平计划和“缅甸拥有和领导的解决方案”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asean-foreign-ministers-back-myanmar-owned-led-solution-crisis-2024-01-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 09:56:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>外国出生的居民因涉嫌种族歧视在日本提起诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/foreign-born-residents-file-suit-japan-over-alleged-racial-profiling-2024-01-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据原告律师称，这是日本第一起此类诉讼，且正值进入日本的外国工人数量急剧增加之际。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/foreign-born-residents-file-suit-japan-over-alleged-racial-profiling-2024-01-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 09:38:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦和伊朗扩大安全合作，摆脱导弹袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/pakistan-iran-agree-expand-security-cooperation-after-missile-strikes-2024-01-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦和伊朗周一表示，他们尊重彼此的主权和领土完整，并将扩大安全合作，在针锋相对的导弹袭击他们所说的激进目标后，寻求修复关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/pakistan-iran-agree-expand-security-cooperation-after-missile-strikes-2024-01-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 09:29:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾否认与中国有“特殊安排”向礁石上的部队提供补给</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-denies-special-arrangements-with-china-supply-troops-reef-2024-01-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾周一否认中国与马尼拉达成“临时特别安排”，允许向占领南海争议岛礁的菲律宾军队运送物资，称其为“凭空想象”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-denies-special-arrangements-with-china-supply-troops-reef-2024-01-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 08:58:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
